io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.annotation

Class ProcessorInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.annotation.ProcessorInterface
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class ProcessorInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods the annotation processor code generator uses that rely on minecraft classes. This is here to ensure compatibility between different mappings as these methods are not remapped. THIS IS NOT MEANT TO BE USED BY ANYTHING ELSE BUT THE ANNOTATION PROCESSOR AND THEREFORE MARKED DEPRECATED.
